Module org.apache.jena.core
Package org.apache.jena.enhanced

Class EnhGraph

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.enhanced.EnhGraph
Direct Known Subclasses:
ModelCom
public class EnhGraph extends Object
EnhGraph wraps a plain graph and contains enhanced nodes that wrap the plain nodes of the plain graph. All the enhanced nodes in the enhanced graph share the same polymorphic personality.

    • equals

      public final boolean equals(Object o)
      An enhanced graph is equal to another graph g iff the underlying graphs are equal. This is deemed to be a complete and correct interpretation of enhanced graph equality, which is why this method has been marked final.

      Note that this equality test does not look for correspondence between the structures in the two graphs. To test whether another graph has the same nodes and edges as this one, use isIsomorphicWith(org.apache.jena.enhanced.EnhGraph).

      Overrides:
      equals in class Object
      Parameters:
      o - An object to test for equality with this node
      Returns:
      True if o is equal to this node.
      See Also:
      • isIsomorphicWith(org.apache.jena.enhanced.EnhGraph)
